snippet.title: हिंदी माध्यम का सर्वश्रेष्ठ रिज़ल्ट । Dr Vikas Divyakirti | UPSC CSE 2022। Drishti IAS
snippet.description:
प्रिय व्यूअर्स, 

हिंदी मीडियम से अभी तक 54 सिलेक्शन्स मिल चुके हैं। यह पिछले 20-25 वर्षों का सर्वश्रेष्ठ परिणाम है। 

पिछले साल हिंदी मीडियम से कुल 24 सिलेक्शन्स हुए थे। इस साल हमारी 50 की कोशिश थी। 

अगले साल 75 की कोशिश रहेगी और 100 का सपना!

सभी सफल अभ्यर्थियों को ढेरों बधाई 💐💐


=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵
𝐒𝐮𝐛𝐬𝐜𝐫𝐢𝐛𝐞 𝐃𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐢 𝐈𝐀𝐒 𝐒𝐡𝐨𝐫𝐭𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐧𝐧𝐞𝐥 :

डिजिटल संसार में अधिक रचनात्मक भागीदारी के उद्देश्य से हमने Drishti IAS Shorts के रूप में एक और यूट्यूब चैनल लॉन्च किया है। शॉर्ट्स के लिये निर्धारित समय-सीमा में, इसमें हम रोचक कंटेंट प्रस्तुत करेंगे।

इस लिंक पर जाकर सब्सक्राइब करें: https://drishti.link/Drishti-IAS-Shorts

=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵

𝐆𝐒 𝐅𝐨𝐮𝐧𝐝𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐂𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐬𝐞 (𝐏𝐫𝐞𝐥𝐢𝐦𝐬 + 𝐌𝐚𝐢𝐧𝐬) 𝐎𝐧𝐥𝐢𝐧𝐞/𝐏𝐞𝐧𝐝𝐫𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐌𝐨𝐝𝐞:

👉 For 𝐟𝐞𝐞, 𝐀𝐝𝐦𝐢𝐬𝐬𝐢𝐨𝐧 and 𝐨𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫 𝐝𝐞𝐭𝐚𝐢𝐥𝐬 of this course visit this link: https://drishti.link/Online-Course or download the 𝐃𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐢 𝐋𝐞𝐚𝐫𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐀𝐩𝐩.

👉 To know the 𝐝𝐞𝐭𝐚𝐢𝐥𝐬 𝐨𝐫 𝐭𝐨 𝐫𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫 through our website click on this link: https://drishti.link/foundation-course

👉 𝐓𝐨 𝐠𝐞𝐭 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐝𝐞𝐭𝐚𝐢𝐥𝐬 about this 𝐖𝐡𝐚𝐭𝐬𝐀𝐩𝐩 𝐨𝐫 𝐒𝐌𝐒 "𝐆𝐒" on this number: 𝟗𝟑𝟏𝟏𝟒𝟎𝟔𝟒𝟒𝟐

=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵

𝐏𝐞𝐧𝐝𝐫𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐂𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐬𝐞𝐬 (𝐇𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐢 𝐋𝐢𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐨𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫𝐬):

👉 For 𝐟𝐞𝐞, 𝐀𝐝𝐦𝐢𝐬𝐬𝐢𝐨𝐧 and 𝐨𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫 𝐝𝐞𝐭𝐚𝐢𝐥𝐬 of 𝐏𝐞𝐧𝐝𝐫𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐂𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐬𝐞 (Hindi Literature and other courses): http://bit.ly/2vGNj72

localized.description:
प्रिय व्यूअर्स,

snippet.title: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Weekly Reliv
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is here to entertain and make you all laugh once again! Watch the characters try to live their day-to-day lives and in return make everyone on a laughter ride! Watch these specially curated clips and relax.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा  #SonyPAL

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises

Watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Weekly Reliv

snippet.title: Living like Wednesday Addams for 24 hours.. *dancing like her in public*🥲
snippet.description:
In today's hilarious and spooky challenge, I decided to immerse myself in the world of the iconic Wednesday Addams from The Addams Family. Get ready to join me as I live, eat, and play like Wednesday Addams for a full 24 hours!

🖤 Living Like Wednesday Addams:
From her dark sense of humor to her gothic fashion style, Wednesday Addams is a character that has captivated audiences for generations. I couldn't resist the opportunity to step into her shoes and experience a day in her peculiar and macabre world.

🍽️ Creepy Cuisine:
To fully embrace the challenge, I had to indulge in the kinds of spooky and unconventional meals that Wednesday Addams would enjoy. Watch as I explore unusual recipes and try eerie treats that are sure to make your skin crawl!

🎮 Spooky Games and Activities:
Wednesday Addams is known for her love of all things eerie and mysterious. Join me as I engage in some chilling games and activities that capture the essence of Wednesday's unique and dark interests. From board games with a twist to peculiar hobbies, you won't want to miss the fun!

💀 Fashion Transformation:
No challenge would be complete without a fashion transformation! Watch as I recreate Wednesday Addams' signature look, from her iconic braided pigtails to her monochromatic wardrobe. I'll show you how to achieve her creepy-chic style using items you may already have in your closet.


Join me on this wild and wacky adventure as I channel my inner Wednesday Addams for a full 24 hours. Get ready for laughs, scares, and plenty of bizarre moments that will keep you entertained throughout the video!


🔔 Turn on notifications to never miss an upload!

snippet.title: Dino James - Boyfriend Reprise | Music Prod. by @BluishMusic
snippet.description:
"Boyfriend Reprise" the song offers a raw and honest plea of running away from toxicity, own thoughts, insecure nature of an individual in a relationship. This reprise version is a nonchalant expression of Dino James wherein through his powerful lyrics and emotional delivery, Dino James sheds light on an important issue that is often overlooked and ignored in our society. Dino James has a strong message for the ones who are facing such insecurities, "You shouldn't let such insecurities consume you or bother you choose to walk away and cut-off this insecurities when needed"

hi.title: Dino James - Boyfriend Reprise | Music Prod. by @BluishMusic
hi.description:
"Boyfriend Reprise" the song offers a raw and honest plea of running away from toxicity, own thoughts, insecure nature of an individual in a relationship. This reprise version is a nonchalant expression of Dino James wherein through his powerful lyrics and emotional delivery, Dino James sheds light on an important issue that is often overlooked and ignored in our society. Dino James has a strong message for the ones who are facing such insecurities, "You shouldn't let such insecurities consume you or bother you choose to walk away and cut-off this insecurities when needed"

snippet.title: Cheetah की मौत का कैसे बदला लेगी Karishma Singh || Maddam Sir - Ep.124
snippet.description:
Cheetah की मौत का कैसे बदला लेगी Karishma Singh || Maddam Sir - Ep.124

Show Name – Maddam Sir
Star Cast – Gulki Joshi, Shilpa Shinde, Yukti Kapoor, Sonali Naik, Bhavika Sharma, Pankhuri Awasthy Rode, Priyanshu Singh, and Ajay Jadhav
Produced By – Jay Mehta

#MaddamSir #मैड्डमसर #comedy 

About The Show:
-----------------------------
Set in Lucknow the show is based in one such all-women Police station made by 4 beautiful quirky women. Pushpa, the oldest of them, is the head constable who tries to balance her life between home and work. Karishma, the Sub Inspector, is fish out of the water as she is at loggerheads with the philosophy of the police station. She beats before she talks but now she has to solve all cases through reconciliation. Santosh Sharma is a young new recruit and a typical lonely girl in the city. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution is most unusual. The characters and the cases add to the fun and humor of the show. While Pushpa and Karishma are the saas-bahu duo, who keep us entertained by their Squabbles, it is Haseena - Karishma's ideological differences that add to the drama madam and comedy

snippet.title: Brahmanandam Super Comedy Scene | Soggadu Telugu Movie | SP Shorts
snippet.description:
Brahmanandam Super Comedy Scene | Soggadu Telugu Movie | SP Shorts

Soggadu is a 2005 Indian Telugu-language romance film produced by D. Suresh on Suresh Productions banner. Directed by Ravi Babu, it stars Tarun and Aarthi Agarwal in lead roles. With special appearances by Venkatesh, Srikanth , Shriya Saran and Sumanth. Soggadu won good critical appreciation and technical acclaim for the director Ravi Babu. This film was remade in Hindi as Ajab Prem Ki Ghazab Kahani (2009) and in Bengali as Mon Je Kore Uru Uru (2010).

Directed by :  Ravi Babu
Written by  :      Nivas (dialogues)
Screenplay by :  Paruchuri Brothers
Story by :  Ravi Babu
Produced by : D. Suresh Babu,  D. Rama Naidu (presents)
Starring          : Tarun, Aarthi Agarwal, Jugal Hansraj
Cinematography :  Loganathan Srinivasan
Edited by :  Anthony
Music by :  Chakri
Production Company : Suresh Productions
Release date :  31 March 2005

snippet.title: Kritika Mishra, IAS, Rank-66 | UPSC Topper 2022  | Hindi Medium | Mock Interview | Drishti IAS
snippet.description:
Kritika Mishra has secured 66th rank in UPSC CSE exam 2022. The mock interview she has given in Drishti IAS institute has been uploaded on Drishti IAS Channel. We extend our heartiest congratulations to Kritika Mishra on this great achievement. We feel immense pleasure to be a part of her beautiful journey and once again we wish her all the very best for a bright future.
As we all know that UPSC CSE Mock Interviews are a great medium to understand the various dimensions of the Personality Test conducted by UPSC. These Mock Interviews not only familiarize the aspirants with the actual process of UPSC Interviews but also help in identifying the areas that a candidate needs to work upon. Even though one can imagine oneself in a UPSC Interview setting, it is strongly recommended that you watch these Mock Interviews and learn from the experiences of IAS toppers, so that you give your best shot when you reach the interview stage of examination.
We hope that this video of the UPSC IAS Mock Interview will help you understand the approach one should have to tackle the various kinds of questions asked by the panel members.

कृतिका मिश्रा ने 2022 की यूपीएससी परीक्षा में 66वीं रैंक हासिल की है। इन्होंने दृष्टि संस्थान में जो मॉक इंटरव्यू दिया था उसे दृष्टि आई.ए.एस चैनल पर अपलोड किया गया है। हम इस उपलब्धि पर कृतिका मिश्रा को हार्दिक बधाई देते हैं। हम उनकी इस सुंदर यात्रा का हिस्सा बनकर बेहद खुशी महसूस कर रहे हैं और एक बार फिर हम उनके उज्ज्वल भविष्य के लिये उन्हें शुभकामनाएँ देते हैं। 
हम सभी जानते हैं कि मॉक इंटरव्यू संघ लोक सेवा आयोग द्वारा आयोजित व्यक्तित्व परीक्षण (Personality Test) के विभिन्न आयामों को समझने का एक अच्छा माध्यम है। ये मॉक इंटरव्यू न केवल उम्मीदवारों को यूपीएससी साक्षात्कार की वास्तविक प्रक्रिया से परिचित कराते हैं, बल्कि उन क्षेत्रों की पहचान करने में भी मदद करते हैं जिन पर उम्मीदवार को मेहनत करने की आवश्यकता होती है। आप चाहें तो यूपीएससी साक्षात्कार में खुद की कल्पना कर सकते हैं। साथ ही, हम दृढ़ता से अनुशंसा करते हैं कि आप इन मॉक इंटरव्यूज को देखें और आईएएस टॉपर्स के अनुभवों से सीखें ताकि जब आप परीक्षा के साक्षात्कार चरण में पहुँचें, तो आप अपना सर्वश्रेष्ठ प्रदर्शन कर सकें। 
हम आशा करते हैं कि यूपीएससी आईएएस मॉक इंटरव्यू का यह वीडियो आपको यह समझने में मदद करेगा कि पैनल के सदस्यों द्वारा पूछे गए विभिन्न प्रकार के प्रश्नों से निपटने के लिए आपको क्या दृष्टिकोण अपनाना चाहिए।

snippet.title: Bhide ने किया Jetha पर Ball से वार | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

In this episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah, Bhide and Jethalal select their teams for Gokuldham Premier League (GPL). All the society members start preparing for the match. It is also decided that the losing captain will clean the society with the help of a broom. 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 176
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of TMKOC - Revisit The Journey: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSkLfD49YxG8YsjmWdKNU0r

Bhide ने किया Jetha पर Ball से वार | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

Episode 3777: Name Voting
--------------------------------------------------------
The entire Gokuldham society attends Popatlal's name-changing ceremony, which he arranges in a magnificent manner. Everyone is impressed by Popatlal's lavish meal presentations. When Taarak sees the tangy pani puri stand, he starts to drool. Madhavi enters the stage and makes a startling announcement. Popatlal later breaks down in tears and says he never wanted to change his name. Additionally, he recalls his Kanta Bua (aunty), who gave him this name. Will Popatlal now reconsider his choice? Remain tuned!

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 05 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Nimra Khan - 22nd May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 05 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Nimra Khan - 22nd May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

snippet.title: Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 07 Teaser - 23rd May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 07 Teaser - 23rd May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Imran Abbas as Shani

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 06 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Nimra Khan - 23rd May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.description:
Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 693 & 694 | Recap

Sartaj notices Ekam suffering in silence and persuades him to move on with his life. Meanwhile, Rupi gets another panic attack during Naaz's first rasoi. She uses this to her advantage and orders him to sign the property deed. Will he comply?

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?

snippet.title: PART 1 - RAHUL DUA IN AMERICA - TIMEZONES, TAP WATER & COSTCO | StandUp Comedy by Rahul Dua | USA
snippet.description:
EDIT:  "Oh Hello!" Australia and NZ tour (Jun'23) tickets: https://linktr.ee/RahulDuaTour
"New Comedy Special 2023-24" UK-EU Tour (Aug-Sep'23) tickets: https://linktr.ee/RahulDuaTour

This video was shot in Boston, Massachusetts on 25th March, 2023. 
It was my first ever visit to the USA and I am very exited to present to you some of my favourite observations & experiences from the days I spent in the US as part of my Stand Up World Tour. 
These are observational jokes rehearsed and delivered in 12-13 shows, unlike conventional stand up content which takes a couple of years to perfect. So need all your love, appreciation and support as I deal with timezone differences, the concept of drinkable tap water and Costco as the one stop shop for all possible needs. Drop in a LIKE and SHARE the video if you've had similar experiences or know someone who went through something similar, and COMMENT with your favourite joke from the video. 
Part 2 out soon, so stay tuned!

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 47 Teaser - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 47 Teaser - 18th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

FULL VIDEO | RadhaKrishn Raasleela Part - 553 | Dwarka Mein Maharshi Vedvyaas Ka Aagaman #starbharat 

FULL VIDEO | RadhaKrishn Raasleela Part - 553 | Dwarka Mein Maharshi Vedvyaas Ka Aagaman #starbharat

►*About*
-------------

RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!


#radhakrishn #starbharat #dildekedekhozara #mythology #राधाकृष्ण
#radhakrishna #sumallika #mallikasingh #radha

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Kya Loge Tum | Akshay Kumar | Amyra Dastur | BPraak | Jaani | Arvindr Khaira | Zohrajabeen
snippet.description:
Desi Melodies presents in association with Cape Of Good Films & Azeem Dayani the first single, 'Kya Loge Tum,' from B Praak's highly anticipated debut album, "Zohrajabeen." The star-studded team of B Praak, Jaani, Arvindr Khaira, and Akshay Kumar reunites for the first time since the pop-culture-defining songs 'Filhall' and 'Filhaal 2.'

The emotionally charged lyrics written by Jaani, along with his heart-wrenching composition, add an extra layer of depth to the already powerful track produced by B Praak himself. Arvindr Khaira takes it to the next level with his visionary direction, featuring Akshay Kumar and Amyra Dastur's palpable chemistry that will leave you wanting more.

Listen to 'Kya Loge Tum' - https://bit.ly/KyaLogeTum

Featuring - Akshay Kumar and Amyra Dastur

snippet.title: Prime Minister Narendra Modi emplanes for Australia after concluding PNG visit
snippet.description:
PM Modi departed for Australia from Papua New Guinea on May 22. He was accorded with ‘Guard of Honour’ before his departure. The Prime Minister began his last leg of the three-nation visit. PM Modi was in Papua New Guinea for the 3rd FIPIC Summit. PNG conferred the ‘Companion of the order of Logohu’ to PM Modi. He was given the accolade for championing cause of unity of Pacific Island countries. The honour comes immediately after Fiji conferred their highest civilian award to him. Notably, only a handful of Non-Fijians have received ‘Companion of the Order of Fiji’ honour so far.  

#NarendraModi #Australia #PapuaNewGuinea

snippet.title: S8E4 | David Warner | Breakfast with Champions ft Gaurav Kapur | @skodaindia ​
snippet.description:
He has a habit of getting people to take notice of him. Right from a sensational international debut in 2009, to a double ton in his 100th Test match, it's been an incredible career. 

He's had a fantastic run in India as well, being the most successful overseas cricketer on the field as well as off the field, with nearly 10 million fans eagerly awaiting his fun dance video on social media.

David Warner gets intimate with Gaurav Kapur in this episode of Skoda presents Breakfast with Champions, and tells us about his culturally diverse upbringing that led to him becoming the man he is, how he became so mentally strong, how he coped with all the controversies in his life, and why no one should ever prank Ricky Ponting.

This episode tastes best with a beer while you slip the shrimp on the Barbie.

#GauravKapur #Cricket #SkodaDrivesBWC #BreakfastWithChampions #DavidWarner #IPL #DelhiCapitals #Warner

►*About*
-------------

RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

Watch More Like This : https://www.youtube.com/starplus/videos


*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: Phir Aur Kya Chahiye| Zara Hatke Zara Bachke| Vicky K, Sara Ali K, Arijit Singh,Sachin-Jigar,Amitabh
snippet.description:
Lose yourself in the magic of love with the much-awaited song "Phir Aur Kya Chahiye'' from the film 'Zara Hatke Zara Bachke'. Mesmerizing vocals of Arijit Singh perfectly complement the intense chemistry between Sara Ali Khan and Vicky Kaushal. The music is composed by the talented duo Sachin-Jigar, and is here to make your heart skip a beat!

The soulful lyrics penned by Amitabh Bhattacharya will make you feel the love. A must watch movie directed by Laxman Utekar, featuring Sara Ali Khan and Vicky Kaushal.

Listen on other OTT platforms:
Spotify : https://spoti.fi/42IIHHY

Mix & Mastered By Eric Pillai - FSOB Studios
Assistant Mix Engineer- Michael Edwin Pillai
Recording Engineer - Swar Mehta - White Noise studios

toh bhi tu hi
